parameters: \n<Lyric>"Hey, should we take a break? I'm getting hungry."

\n<Ameria>"Oh Lyric, you always say that... But you're right. It's a
bit early, but let's have lunch... Is that okay with you,
Roselitte-san?"
\n<Roselitte>"Yes... I need to have my injuries looked at anyway."

\n<Roselitte>"I don't want to hear that from someone who's complaining
about being hungry."

\n<Roselitte>"Truly... It's just a simple vegetable soup, but it tastes
so refined..."

\n<Ameria>"Ehehe♪ I'm glad to hear that. Next time, I'll treat you to
a proper meal."
\n<Roselitte>"Then, may I request that bread? Freshly baked, please."

\n<Ameria>"Ah, right! Then we should choose a dish that goes well with
it. What should I make..."
\n<Lyric>"Roselitte has had it too. Ameria's bread."

\n<Roselitte>"Yes. On the night we met in Abel. It wasn't freshly baked
then, but it was a very fragrant bread."
\n<Lyric>"Heh, I've had it many times. Freshly baked."
\n<Ameria>"You two are exaggerating over just a loaf of bread."

\n<Roselitte>"Not at all. It's on par with the bread from any local
baker, not to mention what my personal chef makes."
\n<Lyric>"Wow, casually bragging about being someone important."

\n<Lyric>"With that attitude, you won't be popular! You need to be
humble and able to cook like Ameria."
\n<Roselitte>"Hmph. When did I ever say I couldn't cook?"
\n<Ameria>"Roselitte-san cooks too? I want to try it!"

\n<Roselitte>"Yes, let's make it next time. There's something quick and
popular among my subordinates."
\n<Lyric>"...Maybe I should try learning to cook too..."

\n<Ameria>"It's about my treatment... How is it going? Is there
anything strange happening?"

\n<Roselitte>"...No. I do feel a bit spaced out during the treatment, but
there's nothing strange. On the contrary, I think my
condition is improving."

\n<Ameria>"I see... that's good then. Sorry for asking something
weird."

\n<Ameria>"If you need me again, just call out. Don't push yourself
until then, okay?"
\n<Ameria>"...Understood. Then, please stay still for a little while."
\n<Roselitte>"No, I'll ask for your help again later."
\n<Ameria>"Understood. Make sure not to overdo it."
\n<Ameria>"Yes.... Are you okay? Are you sure there's nothing wrong?"

Thanks to the treatment, the HP cost for skills has been
reduced!
\n<Roselitte>"Let's have Ameria look at our injuries before we move on."

\n<Ameria>"Um, Roselitte-san. About my treatment... How is it? Is
there anything strange happening?"

\n<Roselitte>"...No. I feel a bit spaced out, but nothing strange. On the
contrary, I think I'm feeling better."

\n<Ameria>"I see... that's good then. Sorry for asking something
weird."

\n<Ameria>"Are you feeling alright? Let me know if anything feels
off."
\n<Ameria>"...Understood. Then please stay still for a little while."
\n<Roselitte>"No, I'll ask for your help again later."

\n<Roselitte>"Yes, thanks to Ameria's care, I've been feeling much
better."

\n<Roselitte>"The doctors on the mainland weren't very helpful... I'm
truly grateful."
\n<Lyric>"Wow, so Ameria's medical techniques are that good?"

\n<Roselitte>"The other healers just ran tests and didn't do much in
terms of treatment."

\n<Roselitte>"Once this is all over, would you consider working as a
healer on the mainland, Ameria?"

\n<Ameria>"...If it means Roselitte-san's injuries get better, that's
more than enough for me.♪"
\n<Roselitte>"Let's have Ameria look at our injuries before we move on."
